---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import AvatarCode from '../../components/AvatarCode.astro'
---

<Layout
	title='About Exavatar - The Future of Avatar Generation'
	description='Learn about Exavatar, the powerful avatar generation API built with modern web technologies. Discover our mission to make beautiful avatars accessible to everyone.'>
	<header
		class='grid-box box-height-2 col-[1/13] row-[3/5] grid grid-flow-row auto-rows-min content-center md:col-[3/11] md:row-[2/4]'>
		<h1 class='content-end text-center text-3xl font-semibold'>About Exavatar</h1>
		<p class='text-md line-clamp-2 content-center text-center text-balance'>
			The future of avatar generation is here
		</p>
	</header>

	<main class='contents'>
		<section class='contents'>
			<h2
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[6/7] content-center px-4 text-2xl font-semibold md:col-[3/11] md:row-[5/6]'>
				Our Mission
			</h2>
			<p
				class='grid-box box-height-4 col-[2/12] row-[7/11] content-center overflow-auto px-4 text-pretty md:col-[3/11] md:row-[6/10]'>
				We believe that every application deserves beautiful, unique avatars. Our mission is to
				provide developers with the most powerful, flexible, and easy-to-use avatar generation API
				available today.
				<br /><br />
				Built with modern web technologies like Deno and Astro, Exavatar delivers lightning-fast performance
				while maintaining the highest standards of code quality and developer experience.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class='contents'>
			<h2
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[12/13] content-center px-4 text-2xl font-semibold md:col-[3/11] md:row-[11/12]'>
				Why Choose Exavatar?
			</h2>
			<h3
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[13/14] content-center px-4 text-lg font-medium md:col-[3/11] md:row-[12/13]'>
				ðŸš€ Lightning Fast
			</h3>
			<p
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[14/15] content-center overflow-auto px-4 text-sm md:col-[3/11] md:row-[13/14]'>
				Built on Deno's high-performance runtime, our API generates avatars in milliseconds.
			</p>
			<h3
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[15/16] content-center px-4 text-lg font-medium md:col-[3/11] md:row-[14/15]'>
				ðŸŽ¨ Highly Customizable
			</h3>
			<p
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[16/17] content-center overflow-auto px-4 text-sm md:col-[3/11] md:row-[15/16]'>
				Choose from multiple styles, colors, sizes, and formats to match your brand perfectly.
			</p>
			<h3
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[17/18] content-center px-4 text-lg font-medium md:col-[3/11] md:row-[16/17]'>
				ðŸ”§ Developer Friendly
			</h3>
			<p
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[18/19] content-center overflow-auto px-4 text-sm md:col-[3/11] md:row-[17/18]'>
				Simple REST API with comprehensive documentation and interactive playground.
			</p>
			<h3
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[19/20] content-center px-4 text-lg font-medium md:col-[3/11] md:row-[18/19]'>
				ðŸ“± Always Available
			</h3>
			<p
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[20/21] content-center overflow-auto px-4 text-sm md:col-[3/11] md:row-[19/20]'>
				Deployed on Deno Deploy for 99.9% uptime and global edge distribution.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class='contents'>
			<h2
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[22/23] content-center px-4 text-2xl font-semibold md:col-[3/11] md:row-[21/22]'>
				Technology Stack
			</h2>
			<p
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[23/24] content-center overflow-auto px-4 md:col-[3/11] md:row-[22/23]'>
				Exavatar is built with modern web technologies to ensure performance, reliability, and
				developer experience:
			</p>
			<ul
				class='grid-box box-height-3 col-[2/12] row-[24/27] list-disc content-center space-y-2 overflow-auto px-4 pl-10 md:col-[3/11] md:row-[23/26]'>
				<li><strong>Deno</strong> - Modern, secure runtime for JavaScript and TypeScript</li>
				<li><strong>Astro</strong> - Fast, content-focused web framework</li>
				<li><strong>TypeScript</strong> - Type-safe development for better code quality</li>
				<li>
					<strong>Tailwind CSS</strong> - Utility-first CSS framework for rapid UI development
				</li>
				<li><strong>Deno Deploy</strong> - Serverless platform for global edge deployment</li>
			</ul>
		</section>

		<section class='contents'>
			<h2
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[28/29] content-center px-4 text-2xl font-semibold md:col-[3/11] md:row-[27/28]'>
				Open Source
			</h2>
			<p
				class='grid-box box-height-2 col-[2/12] row-[29/31] content-center overflow-auto px-4 md:col-[3/11] md:row-[28/30]'>
				Exavatar is proudly open source! We believe in transparency and community collaboration. You
				can explore our codebase, contribute improvements, or report issues on GitHub.
			</p>
			<div
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[31/32] content-center space-x-4 px-4 md:col-[3/11] md:row-[30/31]'>
				<a
					href='https://github.com/gitchaell/exavatar'
					target='_blank'
					class='btn btn-primary'>
					View on GitHub
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<section class='contents'>
			<h2
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[33/34] content-center px-4 text-2xl font-semibold md:col-[3/11] md:row-[32/33]'>
				Get Started
			</h2>
			<p
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[34/35] content-center overflow-auto px-4 md:col-[3/11] md:row-[33/34]'>
				Ready to generate your first avatar? Try our API now:
			</p>
			<AvatarCode
				code='https://exavatar.deno.dev/api/avatar?set=animals&id=dinosaur'
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[35/36] content-center px-4 md:col-[3/11] md:row-[34/35]'
			/>
			<div
				class='grid-box box-height-1 col-[2/12] row-[36/37] content-center space-x-4 px-4 md:col-[3/11] md:row-[35/36]'>
				<a
					href='/playground'
					class='btn btn-primary'>
					Try Playground
				</a>
				<a
					href='/docs'
					class='btn btn-secondary'>
					Read Docs
				</a>
			</div>
			<div class='box-height-10 col-[2/12] row-[37/47] md:col-[3/11] md:row-[36/46]'></div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
